{"tid":1728201,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對家開始扮好人了！","createTime":"2019-11-16T18:41:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T18:46:10.000Z","uid":273353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"79e84dca5f32b85c7fe40354b39635b80e940168","tid":1728201,"uid":273353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T18:41:25.000Z","msg":"和理非到我地岀場了！港豬們睇下下面遲早到你，但可以為你岀聲的人死燃曬了！<br />\n<br />\n起初他們（納粹）追殺共產主義者的時候，我沒有說話&mdash;&mdash;因為我不是共產主義者；<br />\n<br />\n接着他們追殺猶太人的時候，我沒有說話&mdash;&mdash;因為我不是猶太人；<br />\n<br />\n後來他們追殺工會成員的時候，我沒有說話&mdash;&mdash;因為我不是工會成員；<br />\n<br />\n此後他們追殺天主教徒的時候，我沒有說話&mdash;&mdash;因為我是新教教徒；<br />\n<br />\n最後他們奔我而來，那時已經沒有人能為我說話了。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;馬丁&middot;尼莫拉牧師《我沒有說話》"},{"pid":"685544d13b758191317e383bd06c8aeecc27b0ab","tid":1728201,"uid":273353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T18:43:06.000Z","msg":"幾時來個幾百萬人大遊行啊！"},{"pid":"8c3a70c5fcd108ec0e368408350451ed94d70774","tid":1728201,"uid":273353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T18:44:27.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"1e8f0c409ab6792b4921e0310010b6f1af5ab736","tid":1728201,"uid":273353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T18:46:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}